<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
            <h1 class="my-4 text-center">User Guide for New Companies</h1>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">1. Register and Login</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Register an account on our platform using your email and password. After you've registered, log into your account.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card my-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">2. Create Your Company Profile</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Click on the "Create New Company" button to begin setting up your company profile. Ensure all information is accurately filled in and capitalized where necessary. This includes the Company Name, Contact Information, Address, Website, Operating Hours, About, and Category.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card my-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">3. Optimize Your Company Profile</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Make your company more visible on our platform by using relevant keywords in your description, keeping your information up to date, and responding promptly to user contacts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card my-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">4. Monitor Your Company's Performance</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Keep an eye on how your company is doing on our platform. We offer various metrics such as views, contacts, and ratings. Use this information to understand how users are interacting with your company profile and adjust your strategy as needed.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
